missionEventData.data1:
One TIE Fighter from Alpha, Beta, and Gamma Squadrons will be sent out on patrol around Outpost D-34. 
Your mission is to inspect all cargo carrying vessels as they pass by our station. 
We are on the lookout for Rebel forces that are fleeing from their base on Hoth.
Incoming ships! They are entering the area near Buoy B-18
TIE Fighter Alpha 1, inspect all craft
Mugaari Freighters requesting permission to pass through this sector.
Transports  requesting permission to pass through this sector.
Warning! Illegal cargo located on one of the freighters
Job well done, Alpha 1! You can continue scanning cargo or return to base.
Freighter Group Onece has been inspected.
Freighter Group Dayta has been inspected.
The incoming shuttles have not identified themselves
All TIE Fighters the shuttles are hostile. Intercept at once.
Imperial transports are being dispatched to board the freighter.
All Enemy shuttles have been destroyed.
